&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;BA/BS Degree or similar college-level education.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1-3 years of work experience in Billings and Collections or other accounting-related fields.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work in a fast-paced environment and handle high-volume transactional tasks simultaneously with a high degree of accuracy.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Extremely detail-oriented and process-driven, with focus on efficiency and problem solving.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Flexibility to overlap with U.S. time zones (primarily EST) during critical close periods and for cross-regional collaboration.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong Excel skills; proficiency with MS Office Suite.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Effective written and verbal communication skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactive and goal-oriented with th

