&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Continuous Improvement:&lt;/strong&gt; Actively evaluate the latest Zuora platform features and industry trends to continuously optimize system performance and automate manual accounting workstreams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You Have&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;7+ years of experience&lt;/strong&gt; in subscription management and financial systems, with a strong track record of hands-on platform implementation and team leadership.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Zuora Functional Expertise:&lt;/strong&gt; Deep functional knowledge of &lt;strong&gt;Zuora Billing&lt;/strong&gt; (required) and Zuora Revenue (RevPro) architecture.&lt;/li&gt;
